    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessimus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/1927" key="#Princeps">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> filius
                        dulcis recordationis domni <persName ref="#people/115" key="#Princeps"
                            >Adelchis</persName>, <rs key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <name ref="Heroicus">Heroici</name>
                        <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelis</rs> nostri, tibi <name ref="Aielbard"
                            >Aielbardo</name>
                        <rs key="#fidelisOf">fideli</rs> nostro filius <name ref="Raginaldus"
                            >Raghenaldi</name> integram <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                                >terra</rs> bacua</rs> uno tenientem intus hanc Beneventanam <rs
                            key="#Cities">civitatem</rs>, propinco <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3400"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName>, que fuit <name ref="Angelbertus">Angelperti</name>
                        <rs key="#Freeborn">liberi homini</rs> filius <name ref="Ursus">Ursi</name>,
                            <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >pro eo quod absque heredes mortuus</rs> est, in ea videlicet ratione ut
                        amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum predictam casam cum iam
                        dicta terra tu et heredes tui habere et possidere valeatis, et a nullo ex
                        nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldeis vel a quibuscumque agentibus
                        habeatis aliqua requisitione, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod
                        vero preceptus concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego
                            <persName ref="#people/3468" key="#Notary">Erchemfrid</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Houses #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventi</placeName> primo anno, mense iulio, quarta
                        decima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
